title: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Belgium Waterways, Belgium , 2008
name: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Belgium Waterways, Belgium , 2008
description: This data set was provided by open street maps and shows the waterways, streams, rivers, canals, and other water routes throughout Belgium. Data includes attributes for name, ID, type of feature, and width of the waterway (if available).
